# Public release staging scope.
#
# At this stage, only the public documentation tree, public project tree, and
# root release metadata files are trackable. Top-level build, output, tool,
# scratch, and artifact directories are local preparation artifacts.
/*
!/docs/
!/project/
!/.gitignore
!/.gitattributes
!/LICENSE
!/NOTICE
!/README.md
!/SECURITY.md
!/KNOWN_LIMITATIONS.md
!/RELEASE_TERMS.md
!/THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md
!/SBOM.json
!/REFERENCE_SYSTEMS_AND_IP_BOUNDARY.md
!/public_contract_snapshot

/build/
/build-*/
/cmake-build-*/
/output/
/artifacts/
/dist/
/release/
/public_release_evidence/
/public_audit_summary/
/tmp/
/tools/

/docs/references/
/docs/findings/

CMakeCache.txt
CMakeFiles/
CTestTestfile.cmake
Testing/
project/drivers/**/.gradle/
project/drivers/**/build/
*.o
*.obj
*.a
*.so
*.dylib
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.ilk
*.pyc
__pycache__/
.pytest_cache/
.cache/
.DS_Store
*.log
*.tmp
*.swp

# External reference material in the public repository is limited to
# ScratchBird-owned harnesses, manifests, locators, and CTest wiring. Raw
# upstream regression payloads, downloaded/native tools, upstream source trees,
# source archives, release-packet evidence extracts, and source-acquisition
# payloads stay local/private and must not be tracked.
#
# Keep stale pre-rename external-reference payload locations out of public source.
project/src/**/[d]onor*/
project/src/**/*[d]onor*
project/src/**/*[D]onor*
project/src/**/reference_system*/
project/src/**/*reference_system*
project/src/**/*ReferenceSystem*
project/src/udr/packages/[d]onor*/
project/src/udr/packages/reference*/
docs/documentation/compatibility-emulation/**
docs/**/*[d]onor*
docs/**/*[D]onor*
docs/**/*reference-system*
docs/**/*ReferenceSystem*
project/docs/**/*[d]onor*
project/docs/**/*[D]onor*
project/docs/**/*reference-system*
project/docs/**/*ReferenceSystem*

# Draft-documentation work products belong in private tracking, not the public
# release documentation tree. Keep product-facing draft pages trackable.
docs/documentation/draft/audit_reports/**
docs/documentation/draft/audit_*.md
docs/documentation/draft/combined*.md
docs/documentation/draft/file_listing*.txt
docs/documentation/draft/**/Notes.md
docs/documentation/draft/**/MGA.md
docs/documentation/draft/**/MGA.pdf
docs/documentation/draft/**/.generation_state.json
docs/documentation/draft/**/.claude/**

project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**/
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**/regression/
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**/regression/PUBLIC_REGRESSION_SCOPE.md
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**/regression/*_CANDIDATE.md
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**/regression/*_MANIFEST.csv
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_release_acquisition/**/regression/*_INDEX.csv

!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_catalog_seeds/
!project/tests/reference_regression/reference_catalog_seeds/**
project/tests/reference_regression/**/native_tool_harness/tools/**
project/tests/reference_regression/firebird/original_firebird_qa/**

# Pre-rename local payloads may still exist in developer worktrees.
project/tests/[d]onor_regression/[d]onor_release_acquisition/**
project/tests/[d]onor_regression/**/native_tool_harness/tools/**
project/tests/[d]onor_regression/firebird/original_firebird_qa/**

# Temporary private pre-release distribution bundles. These are intentionally
# trackable while the repository remains private and must be removed or moved to
# external release hosting before the first official public source release.
!/packaging/
!/packaging/**
packaging/**/.staging/
packaging/**/__pycache__/
packaging/**/*.tmp
